content: If you are at the May 2019 WGM and using the Python FHIRClient we are having an informal meeting tommorrow: https://chat.fhir.org/#narrow/stream/179218-python/topic/PyFHIR.20side.20chat.20with.20Pascal!!
to clarify we will be meeting on the 2nd floor ( 1 below the main dining room )

Hello, we just pushed updates to the Python FHIR Clients to R$ https://github.com/smart-on-fhir/client-py. If would be helpful would be happy to set-up a Zoom to touch base on getting the Python Clients updated and hear how people are using it.
Alguém poderia me ajudar(help) com a minha proposta de TCC?
